<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The P06 event is a notification that the account is no longer open, that is, no new charges can accrue to this account. This notification is not related to whether or not the account is paid in full. <em>EVN-2 - Recorded Date/Time</em> must contain the account end date.</p>
</div>
